videos.description: Washington RB Myles Gaskin runs towards the sideline and turns it upfield for the 28-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Gaskin gets Washington on the board with TD rush

videos.description: Jake Browning finds Dante Pettis in the corner of the end zone for the Washington touchdown.
videos.headline: Browning throws the corner fade for the TD

videos.description: Myles Gaskin lines up in the shotgun formation then runs the snap in for the 7-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Gaskin scores off the direct snap

videos.description: Washington's Dante Pettis returns the Fresno State punt 77 yards for his eighth career punt-return touchdown.
videos.headline: Pettis has punt-return TD for third straight game

videos.description: Jake Browning with another pass to the corner of the end zone to Dante Pettis for the Huskies touchdown.
videos.headline: Browning connects with Pettis again for the TD

videos.description: Jake Browning connects with Myles Gaskin over the middle for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Washington with one more TD before halftime

videos.description: Jake Browning throws downfield to Dante Pettis who scores the 73-yard touchdown for Washington.
videos.headline: Browning fires deep downfield to Pettis for another TD
